
Snappy
------

apt-get update
snappy --help
snappy info
snappy list -v
snappy list -uv
snappy search docker
sudo snappy install docker
snappy list
snappy info
docker version
docker ps
sudo snappy install hello-world
sudo snappy update ubuntu-core
sudo snappy rollback ubuntu-core
apparmor_status


RancherOS
---------

uname -a
ps | more --> PID 1 system docker
          --> PID X user docker
docker ps
sudo system-docker ps
sudo system-docker logs ntp

sudo rancherctl help
sudo rancherctl os
sudo rancherctl os version
sudo rancherctl os list
sudo rancherctl os upgrade?


CoreOS
------

vagrant up
vagrant ssh core-01
systemctl status etcd2, fleet, flanneld
etcdctl member list
etcdctl ls ...
etcdctl set ... check in another node
etcdctl see flannel network

fleetctl list-units
fleetctl list-machines
create helloworld.service
fleetctl start helloworld.service
check on other machines
